Summary: This ufo appeared in 2 photos I took
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Ormond Beach
There were no other sightings in Ormond Beach on or around April 4th 2013
divs: Sighting DetailsI saw this object after I enlarged a photo I had taken. I took 2 photos, in the first one you can see a speck in the distance of the approach, in the 2nd photo it is quite clear when slightly enlarged. I had been taking a photo of a barge and what it was towing. I have no idea what it is and showed it to other people and no one could id what it is. I'm hoping you can help.I took these photos from my hotel balcony at 4:07pm in Ormond Beach FL.I wasn't aware of the object while i was shooting the picture.
